efault on your profile">Kaoru</span> told that, even though they had troubles and hardships, Asuka and Shinji were very happy together after getting married in his timeline.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroesWantRedheads" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroesWantRedheads">Heroes Want Redheads</a>: It is an Asuka/Shinji fic.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroicBSOD" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroicBSOD">Heroic BSoD</a>:<ul><li> After her <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MindRape" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MindRape">Mind Rape</a>, Asuka was broken and subdued for a long while.</li><li> Shinji had several nervous breakdowns throughout the history, the final one happening right before Third Impact.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroicSacrifice" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroicSacrifice">Heroic Sacrifice</a>: <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">Rei III</span> replaces <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">Rei II</span> right before the battle against the Sixteenth to give the latter a chance to keep living. <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">As a reward, Rei II shares her memories with Rei III in the last moments before her death, and Rei III dies happy, knowing exactly what she's giving her life to protect.</span></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheHerosBirthday" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheHerosBirthday">The Hero's Birthday</a>: The story begins on Shinji's 16th birthday. The first scenes feature Shinji making a celebratory meal, and later that day Shinji meets his new teacher who will change his outlook greatly and for the best.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HesBack" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HesBack">He's Back</a>:<ul><l